{"tid":736066,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「熬夜瘋玩PS4不練球」　外媒揭德國世足慘敗真相","createTime":"2018-07-10T03:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T03:44:26.000Z","uid":148897,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2373bbd432b16c96c9641ea46786ca9db239c1f","tid":736066,"uid":148897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯世足賽即將進入尾聲，回顧本屆賽事話題十足，最大的驚奇之一可能就是上屆冠軍德國隊0：2輸南韓，不僅跌破專家眼鏡、也意外在小組賽就慘遭淘汰，多數球迷把矛頭指向主教練勒夫調度失當，不過近日有媒體報導，德國隊爛到有剩的表現可能和球員瘋玩PS4有關！<br />\n<br />\n根據歐洲發行量最大的《圖片報》獨家消息指出，世界盃期間有多名德國球員把遊戲主機PS4帶到下榻飯店，熬夜狂玩熱門足球遊戲《FIFA18》，結果導致隔天練習精神不振，逼得德國領隊不得不要求飯店切斷無線網路，直言懶散、漫不經心的態度才是德國隊輸球主因，消息傳出引發網友熱烈討論，「難道索尼不用負責嗎！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe4cf9a5e32d2b8a26e7b24eb5e0e2067b7cf82","tid":736066,"uid":148897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/new/1388278/rnews/20180710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2Fnew%2F1388278%2Frnews%2F20180710&d=8K%2FJt68LUXxfc94keT6z5YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=2e33ad28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2Fnew%2F1388278%2Frnews%2F20180710&h=6f414a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/new/1388278/rnews/20180710</a>"},{"pid":"db56ce519803c6e8d13e7e3a8c9160eedfebd735","tid":736066,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2894ff9aa8ef0b23f2fcc72554a0f8113cbed2a1","tid":736066,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a197065ab38aa0e191f36c51397